{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "第十一回\"奇浓嘉嘉普\"主要讲述常笑与王风的对峙。常笑以朝廷官员身份质问王风关于铁恨之死，王风坦然承认与铁恨相识不到一天却愿为其送尸。两人从言语交锋升级为武力冲突，常笑令官差围攻王风，王风以近身功夫轻松击退众人。常笑亲自出手，以峨眉夺命十二剑中的毒剑刺向王风，王风以短剑拼命反击，迫使常笑退让。此后常笑转变态度，透露自己正在调查血鹦鹉案与七年前太平王府珠宝失踪案。王风讲述亲眼目睹铁恨被血鹦鹉害死的经过：血鹦鹉能笑能说话，铁恨因不信其存在而许愿求死，结果如愿以偿。血鹦鹉临走时留下两个愿望给王风。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你还有什么不明白？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那些人要杀我的真正原因，真正要杀我的本来是什么人，现在我仍不怎样明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这其实明白与否，也不要紧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "什么才要紧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我未了的那件事！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "哪件事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "寻找我朋友的尸体，送返他的故乡。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你跟铁恨是朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你们在什么时候认识的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "八九天之前。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "七八天之前他已是个死人，你却是八九天之前认识他，到底你们认识了有没有一个整天。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "认识还不到一天的朋友，你就肯替他卖命了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我认识他虽然还不到一天，知道他却已很久。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "知道他什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "知道他是一个正直的人，我一向佩服正直的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "如果你只是因为这个原因替他卖命，我担保你一定会后悔。正直的人绝不会说谎，而据我所知，在血鹦鹉这件事上，他已经不止一次说谎。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "说谎固然可耻，但若吐露事实足以惹起更大的不幸之下，还是可以原谅的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "铁恨的尸体据说是你带回衙门？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "当时铁恨已死亡？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你肯定他的确已死亡？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "一个人是生是死，我还可以分得出的。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不在，萧老先生工作的时候并不喜欢有人在旁边，他认为那会影响他的工作，其实他就算准许我留下，我也未必愿意留下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还怕呕吐。你难道不知道那是怎样恶心的一回事？",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你当自己是什么东西？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "官！",
      "tone": "傲慢",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你又当我是什么东西？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "平民百姓。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "江湖人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "江湖人不怕官，不受管，也没有官敢管。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我敢管！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "就算敢管，我就算受管，又怎样？我又没有犯法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你没有犯法，却有犯法的嫌疑。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我有什么犯法的嫌疑呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你协助嫌疑的犯人，逍遥法外。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "又一个嫌疑，这嫌疑的犯人又是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "铁恨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "到现在为止，虽然你仍没有来一个自我介绍，我却早已猜到你是谁。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "常笑！毒剑常笑。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你睡在棺材里，消息还这么灵通。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "今天清晨，安子豪来找我说过话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这个人说话未免太多。",
      "tone": "不满",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我还知道一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "也是他说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "那件事我最少已听人说过十次，第一次最少已在五年之前。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "到底什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我还知道你另有一个很吓人的外号，就叫活阎王。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这个外号好不好？",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "好是好，有一点，我却很不明白。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "活阎王顾名思义，是人间的阎王，你怎么连鬼都管到了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你是说铁恨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "僵尸难道不是鬼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你肯定他已变成僵尸？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我没有见过僵尸，却见过尸体，我敢担保他已是一个死人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我连尸体都没有见过，在未见到他的尸体之前，我仍当他是一个活人。你也敢担保自己所说的全都是事实？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "就算是事实，你好像也没有办法。",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你知道我还有一个外号叫做活阎王，却似乎不知道我这个外号怎会得来。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "那是因为你的心够狠，手够辣，剑够毒。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "心狠自然手辣，手辣自然剑毒，这三样其实只是一样，你只说中了一样，还差一样。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "哪一样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "刑够重。在我的重刑之下，我敢担保所听到的一定是事实。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你好像已有意思对我用重刑来迫供？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "只不知你怎样将我拿到重刑之下？",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "想知道还不容易？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_chai_jia",
      "speaker_name": "公差甲",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我们一定好好的让你活动一下。",
      "tone": "阴狠",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但动到刀子我就恕不奉陪，那些东西向来就有碍健康。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_chai_yi",
      "speaker_name": "公差乙",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "只可惜由不得你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我看你并不像疯子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "本来就不像。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那你就应该知道，方才那一来会有什么结果？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你我都变成死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "以你的武功，要招架我那一剑，相信并不难。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "也不易。",
      "tone": "谦虚",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "招架都可以，要闪避当然就更容易的了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "闪避事实就比招架来得容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那你为什么还要跟我拼命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "方才你那一剑是不是存心杀我？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你喜欢跟人拼命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "要看什么人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "有种人明知打他不过，我就会赶紧脚底抹油，可是有种人，算就必死无疑，我也要去跟他拼命。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你所说的一种人，到底是哪一种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "恶人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我好像不是恶人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我看就像了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "无论如何，我都不想再跟你拼命了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你不是说过要将我拿下来，用重刑迫供？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "现在已不必，一个人胆敢拼命，又怎会说谎。你既然没有说谎，我为什么还要多此一举？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "最低限度，你总该将我扣押起来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "因为我已经犯法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "打官差虽然犯法，这件事，却不能归咎于你。我并不是一个完全不讲理的人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "何况要杀你都难，要将你扣押，岂非就更伤脑筋。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "更何况今后很多事说不定我都要借助于你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我还没有意思跟你混在一起。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你可知道我现在在调查什么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "可是关于血鹦鹉那件案子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "也就是七年前太平王府库藏珠宝一夜之间完全神秘失踪的那件案子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "那件案子跟我有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "跟你没有关系，跟你的朋友铁恨却有很大的关系。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "铁恨已死亡。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "死因是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你可曾听过十万神魔为了庆贺魔王的寿诞，聚会'奇浓嘉嘉普'，以十万滴麾血化成一只血鹦鹉，作为他们的贺礼这件事？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "最少已听过十次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "血鹦鹉每隔七年便会降临人间一次，带来三个愿望，只要你看见它，你就能得到那个愿望，无论什么愿望都可实现。现在距离他上次降临人间，已又有七年。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你也相信这种事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我本来不信，现在不能不信。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你看到他了。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "你不信？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁恨也不信，所以他才表示如果看到血鹦鹉，第一个愿望便要它让他死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "结果他真的遇上了血鹦鹉，血鹦鹉真的就让他如愿以偿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "天下的事情有时就是这样子凑巧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这件事你听哪一个说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "当时我正坐在他的对面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你是说目睹着这件事发生？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第一个看见血鹦鹉的还是我，当时我已呼叫他不要回望，甚至扑过去要抱住他的头，但都已太晚。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "血鹦鹉竟会笑？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像人一样的笑，笑声中，充满了一种难言的妖异邪恶，就像它说话的语声一样。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "它还会说话？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "它说了什么？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是同时看见我的，现在他的愿望已实现了，还有两个愿望我会留给你，你等着……",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那只血鹦鹉后来又怎样？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "飞走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你有没有追下去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我倒也想追下去，只可惜我并没有长着翅膀。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "当时你们在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "墓地。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "墓地？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我们是因为追着血奴追到那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    }
  ],
